OL,3,CZero-hours contracts ban will go
OL,4,Cahead, Business Secretary tells ITV
OL,5,CNews
OL,7,FA plan to ban zero-hours contracts is
OL,8,Fgoing ahead, the government has
OL,9,Fconfirmed to ITV News, despite
OL,10,Fwarnings from business about how the
OL,11,Fpolicy could further drive up
OL,12,Funemployment.
OL,14,FA consultation is being launched to
OL,15,Fgather evidence on how to implement
OL,16,Fthe policy before going ahead with the
OL,17,Fban, Business Secretary Peter Kyle
OL,18,Ftold ITV News.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
