OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780473962
OL,3,CZero-hours contracts ban will go
OL,4,Cahead, Business Secretary tells ITV
OL,5,CNews
OL,7,FThe British Retail Consortium and
OL,8,FUKHospitality wrote to Kyle ahead of
OL,9,Fthe consultation being launched,
OL,10,Furging a rethink, saying it would help
OL,11,Favoid a "double whammy of increasing
OL,12,Funemployment and fewer young people
OL,13,Fentering the labour market".
OL,15,F"Across our sectors, concern is deep
OL,16,Fand growing that the current approach
OL,17,Frisks stripping flexibility from the
OL,18,Flabour market at precisely the wrong
OL,19,Fmoment," the letter said.
OL,26,@sD@IOUuD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
