OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780473962
OL,3,CZero-hours contracts ban will go
OL,4,Cahead, Business Secretary tells ITV
OL,5,CNews
OL,7,F"With demand already weakened, poorly
OL,8,Fdesigned guaranteed hours measures
OL,9,Fcould become a tipping point, pushing
OL,10,Femployers to reduce hiring, limit
OL,11,Fhours or withdraw flexible roles
OL,12,Faltogether."
OL,14,FAsked if the policy would discourage
OL,15,Fhiring, Kyle said: "It's completely
OL,16,Fthe opposite. This is about giving
OL,17,Fsecurity in the workforce.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
