PN,31706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780473962
OL,3,CZero-hours contracts ban will go
OL,4,Cahead, Business Secretary tells ITV
OL,5,CNews
OL,7,F"If you don't know how many hours that
OL,8,Fyou have, and you're counting in two
OL,9,Fweeks time that you want to earn a
OL,10,Fcertain amount of money to do a
OL,11,Fcertain thing, or to invest in your
OL,12,Ffamily, or even to eat, and suddenly
OL,13,Fyou can't, then of course you're going
OL,14,Fto want to get away from that employer
OL,15,Fas quickly as you possibly can.
OL,17,F"So this is actually about having
OL,18,Fsecurity in the workplace for the
OL,19,Femployee, but also delivering security
OL,20,Fand predictability for the employer as
OL,21,Fwell."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
