OL,3,CZero-hours contracts ban will go
OL,4,Cahead, Business Secretary tells ITV
OL,5,CNews
OL,7,FIt said eligible workers will be
OL,8,Fentitled to receive reasonable notice
OL,9,Fof their shifts and a payment if their
OL,10,Fshifts are cancelled, moved, or
OL,11,Fcurtailed at short notice.
OL,13,FLast year, TUC general secretary Paul
OL,14,FNowak, said: "Zero-hours contracts
OL,15,Fgive bosses almost total control of
OL,16,Fworkers' earning power and hours `
OL,17,Fmaking it a nightmare for families to
OL,18,Fplan budgets and childcare.
OL,26,@vD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
