PN,31710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780473962
OL,3,CZero-hours contracts ban will go
OL,4,Cahead, Business Secretary tells ITV
OL,5,CNews
OL,7,F"After 14 years of Conservative
OL,8,Fdecline, the era of low-rights, low-
OL,9,Fpay and low-productivity has been
OL,10,Ftested to destruction. Those defending
OL,11,Fthe broken status quo are putting
OL,12,Ftheir own vested interests ahead of
OL,13,Fworking people's lives and ignoring
OL,14,Fthe evidence in front of their eyes."
OL,16,FEmployment Rights Minister Kate
OL,17,FDearden said: "Ending uncertainty over
OL,18,Fhours and pay is one of the best ways
OL,19,Fwe can boost living standards for
OL,20,Fmillions of people and families across
OL,21,Fthe country.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
